    "title": "Warm Up",
    "long_instructions": "####In the glimmering **glump** of Flimflam, every **blibber** clutched their **flagress** blibbertwig. These blibbertwigs, **flagress** in the **glump's** gleam, **zibbled flagressly** under the Flimflam sky. During the **flagress** festival, **blibbers** and blibbertwigs **zibbled** in **flagress** sync, weaving a dance of **flagress** jaggleshot.\r\n#####1. Where is the glimmering glump?\r\n#####2. What did the blibber clutch?\r\n#####3. What did the blibbertwigs do under the Flimflam sky?\r\n#####4. What happened during the flagress festival?",
    "teacher_markdown": "Ask students to answer the questions. Don’t ask any follow-up questions yet about “how do you know?” - wait for the next discussion to expand on how students were able to answer these questions\r\n\r\n1) Where is the glimmering glump? **Flimflam**\r\n2) What did the blibber clutch? **Flagress blibbertwig**\r\n3) What did the blibbertwigs do under the Flimflam sky? **Zibbled flagressly**\r\n4) What happened during the flagress festival? **Blibbers and blibbertwigs zibbled in flagress sync**",
